This project has been cloned from the Rainmeter-Batch-Plugin. You can reference a remote svn project that has been copied localy by using the following config.

[ProjectName]
Measure=Plugin
Plugin=SvnPlugin.dll
LocalRepoPath="C:\sourcecontrol\project"
RepoAlias="Jlog Trunk"
Width=25
LogLimit=20
UpdateDivider=10

Width the is the width of the line.  I use monospaced fonts for me meters so that everything is equaly spaced.
